<definition-item date-revised="2016-01-01"><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">D21G</classification-symbol><definition-title>CALENDERS; ACCESSORIES FOR PAPER-MAKING MACHINES  (winders or rewinders for finished products, means for adjustment of wrinkles or lateral extensions <class-ref scheme="cpc">B65H</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement>
      <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Calenders, smoothing apparatus.</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Rolls for calenders, controlled deflection rolls, doctors, safety devices for paper machinery, damping devices, paper making control systems, devices for threading web tails through a paper machine.</paragraph-text>
